<th class="navbox-group" style="">1951–1975</th>
<td class="navbox-list" style=""><div class="liste-horizontale">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/John_Cockcroft" title="John Cockcroft">Cockcroft</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ernest_Walton" title="Ernest Walton">Walton</a> (1951)</li>
